---
// Hero terminal snippet. Lives in a .astro component (not MDX) so the literal
// newlines inside <pre> are preserved and the URL is not auto-linked.
---

<div class="ar-term">
  <div class="ar-term-bar">
    <span class="ar-dot r"></span><span class="ar-dot y"></span><span class="ar-dot g"></span>
  </div>
  <pre><span class="comment"># clone, build, and audit your setup</span>
<span class="prompt">$</span> git clone https://github.com/agent-rigger/agent-rigger
<span class="prompt">$</span> bun install && bun run build
<span class="prompt">$</span> agent-rigger check
<span class="comment">  [ ok ] guardrails-claude   [ ok ] context-claude</span></pre>
</div>
